        "id": 1144260
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-11-17T20:36:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Probably not the right call. The particular value for SIGABRT probably isn\u0027t that useful either. Now that it\u0027s only for SIGABRT, the best existing status code I can see is STATUS_FATAL_APP_EXIT, so I\u0027ll use that.",
